- F.amily too--
- Hey, is that your mom again?

00:34.234 --> 00:36.395
- ifyou're desperate.
- Someone needs your help, Michael.

00:36.469 --> 00:38.835
Bottom line:
Untilyou figure out who burnedyou...

00:40.974 --> 00:42.965
you're not going anywhere.

00:46.513 --> 00:48.504
[ Michael Narrating ]
There's a good reason covert operatives...

00:48.581 --> 00:51.345
keep their work a secret
from their families.

00:51.418 --> 00:53.818
Once your family knows whatyou do,
you've got problems.

00:56.156 --> 00:58.283
- Best case, they're scared.
- [ Cell Phone Rings ]

00:58.358 --> 01:01.816
Worst case, they figure they can get
into trouble andyou'll get them out of it.

01:01.895 --> 01:04.125
- Yeah.
- [ Nate ] Mi ke, it's your brother.

01:04.197 --> 01:09.362
Listen, uh, I-- I 'm out at Opa-locka Airport,
and I got a situation.

01:09.436 --> 01:12.599
