- [ Foreign Language ]
- Huh?

01:33.760 --> 01:35.728
[ Both Grunting ]

01:38.565 --> 01:40.795
- Yeah?
- Look, man. Firstyou told me to leave.

01:40.867 --> 01:42.960
Nowyou're gonna kill me?
That doesn't even make sense.

01:43.036 --> 01:47.302
All right? I mean, it's gonna takeyou hours to
deal with my body, and then there's the cops.

01:47.373 --> 01:49.500
Come on, man.

01:51.478 --> 01:54.174
