- Didn't need to.

10:20.019 --> 10:22.920
I know a gunrunnerwhen I see one.
They're mypeople.

10:22.989 --> 10:26.186
They ship in a special lubricant,
and the whole hangar smells like it.

10:26.258 --> 10:29.386
[ Sniffs ]
Mmm. There it is.

10:29.462 --> 10:31.589
- No wonder I got my ass kicked.
- Oh, you were lucky.

10:31.664 --> 10:35.760
The old guy had a Desert Eagle
nine-millimeterwith combat grips.

10:35.835 --> 10:38.929
- Ex-Mossad.
- What doyou mean, like Israeli spies?

10:39.005 --> 10:42.805
Sure. Every other retired spook
is an arms dealer.

10:42.875 --> 10:45.810
It's not a bad gig,
ifyou can stand the ex-spooks.

10:47.413 --> 10:49.574
You should probably
call your client.

10:53.119 --> 10:56.088
So--So what do I do, huh?

10:56.155 --> 10:58.180
I mean, I never saw anything
like that there.

10:58.257 --> 11:01.954
No, of course not. They're too smart to keep
anything around that would get them busted.

11:02.028 --> 11:05.259
Listen,Jake. Now that we know what we're
dealing with, we can try to do something.

11:05.331 --> 11:07.925
I should call the police.
I know I'm gonna get busted.

11:08.000 --> 11:11.128
