the only crimes they'll find areyours...

11:11.203 --> 11:14.070
and the Zamars will knowyou turned on them,
and that's not good,Jake.

11:14.140 --> 11:16.938
Take a look at this.

11:17.009 --> 11:19.603
This is howyourjob opened up.

11:19.679 --> 11:21.977
The oldsecuritymanager
diedin a caraccident.

11:22.048 --> 11:25.415
All ofhis brakes just happened to fail
at the same time.

11:27.453 --> 11:29.387
Jesus.

11:29.455 --> 11:32.049
I can't believe this.

11:32.124 --> 11:36.083
I went to a goddamn basketball game with these
people. The seats weren't even that good.

11:36.162 --> 11:39.325
Well, next timeyou accept a bribe,
I'd hold out for courtside seats.

11:39.398 --> 11:41.559
Jake, focus.

11:41.634 --> 11:44.967
- We need to deal with the problem.
- I'm sorry. I don't--

11:45.037 --> 11:47.767
- What do I do?
- Cooperate.

11:47.840 --> 11:50.070
We need to get them
busted with the guns...

11:50.142 --> 11:53.111
and they need to go down in a way
that's unrelated to you...

11:53.179 --> 11:56.808
- so it looks like you had nothing to do with it.
- Get 'em busted with the guns.

11:56.882 --> 12:00.318
- Where are the guns?
- That's what we're gonna go find out.

12:00.453 --> 12:02.648
?? [ Whistling ]

12:06.859 --> 12:08.793
Mike, uh...

12:08.861 --> 12:11.694
