12:11.764 --> 12:14.028
Look, I knowyou've been pushing hard
on this burn notice...

12:14.100 --> 12:17.297
trying to getyourself offthe blacklist
and all, and I understand that.

12:17.369 --> 12:19.701
But I'm gettin' a lot of pressure.

12:19.772 --> 12:21.706
Pressure?
What kind of pressure?

12:21.774 --> 12:23.765
Well, you know, they--

12:23.843 --> 12:29.509
Theywant me to give 'em more.
It's always more. But the thing is that--

12:29.582 --> 12:31.607
Yeah, Sam?

12:31.684 --> 12:33.675
[Sam ]
Oh, hey. Here theygo.

12:38.724 --> 12:40.715
We'll talk about this later.

12:47.299 --> 12:49.665
[Michael Narrating]
One cheap and effective securitymeasure...

12:49.735 --> 12:52.761
is working in an area
with low or no traffic.

12:52.838 --> 12:54.829
Anyone in a car is too obvious...

12:54.907 --> 12:58.468
so you force any would-be
followers to get out and walk.

13:03.783 --> 13:06.217
- They're i n there somewhere.
- Mikey, come on.

13:06.285 --> 13:08.219
I t's 1 0 square blocks.

13:08.287 --> 13:10.482
My cardiovascular fitness
isn't what it used to be.

13:10.556 --> 13:12.615
You know, you never said
we were gonna be walkin'.

13:12.691 --> 13:15.421
Rest frequently,
drink plenty offluids, you'll be fine, Sam.

13:16.762 --> 13:19.731
Okay. Where do I find fluids?

13:41.020 --> 13:42.419
[ Tires Screech ]

