I'm telling you.
There's no one here.

13:49.361 --> 13:51.659
[Ilan ]
Dad thought he saw someone.

13:54.366 --> 13:56.630
- [Ari] There's no one.
- [Ilan ] Well, we have to check.

13:57.937 --> 14:00.030
Ah, I'm getting my shoes dirty.

14:02.441 --> 14:04.875
[ Michael Narrating]
F.ighting is somethingyou want to avoid.

14:04.944 --> 14:07.811
- Onceyou fight someone, he knows your face.
- [Ari ] There is nobody here.

14:07.880 --> 14:10.075
- Shut up.
- You kind ofblowyour cover...

14:10.149 --> 14:11.912
when you hit a guy
with a piece ofrebar.

14:11.984 --> 14:15.044
But when you have no choice,
rebar it is.

14:22.361 --> 14:24.852
- [ Glass Shatters ]
- [ Sam ] Huh?

14:27.132 --> 14:29.896
- [ Bottle Smashes ]
- Send that to Chi na, you sons of bitches!

