Some kind of security?

14:45.248 --> 14:48.012
Hey. Go ahead. Come on.
Shoot me.

14:48.084 --> 14:50.575
I'd thankyou for it.
There's no jobs around here anyway.

14:50.654 --> 14:52.815
Uh, you want to
shoot him, shoot him.

14:52.889 --> 14:54.857
- Let's go.
- Oh, you don't want to shoot him?

14:54.925 --> 14:58.190
Yeah, lovely. Huh?

14:58.261 --> 15:02.925
Yeah. Batter up, huh?
Oh! Strike three! You're laid off!.

15:02.999 --> 15:05.593
Yeah!

15:05.669 --> 15:08.103
They're careful.

15:08.171 --> 15:12.437
Ifwe're gonna get them caught on anything
serious, it's gonna take some more time.

15:13.677 --> 15:15.611
Then I want Melody out ofhere.

15:15.679 --> 15:18.773
I mean, this was my mistake.
She shouldn't have to pay for it.

15:18.848 --> 15:22.045
When the Zamars askwhyyourwife
suddenly left town, what areyou gonna say?

15:24.020 --> 15:27.114
Theycame to see meyesterday.

15:27.190 --> 15:30.785
Theygot anothershipment going out soon.
Theygave me more basketball tickets.

15:30.860 --> 15:33.658
They-- They're
expecting my answer today.

15:33.730 --> 15:35.698
What do I say?

15:35.765 --> 15:40.099
Since they're probably planning on killing you
ifyou say anything else, I'd suggest yes.

15:44.207 --> 15:46.266
Mike, I saved your ass
at the warehouse.

15:46.343 --> 15:49.039
The leastyou could do is have
some decent beer in the fridge.

15:49.112 --> 15:52.479
Next timeyou plan on saving my ass,
tell me before I go to the store.

15:52.549 --> 15:55.143
We still have to find out
where they keep their guns.

15:55.218 --> 15:58.483
I thinkyou're gonna have to do the spy thing,
Mike. Make a new friend.

15:58.555 --> 16:01.388
But I can't get
an angle on this father.

16:01.458 --> 16:04.655
- I mean, his security drill is airtight.
- What about the brothers?

16:04.728 --> 16:07.891
The older brother's the same. He goes to work,
he goes home. There's no way in.

16:07.964 --> 16:11.263
- Younger?
- I talked to him at the hangar.

16:11.334 --> 16:13.268
- He's not so bright.
- I could check him out.

