32:30.042 --> 32:34.604
Why would I want to screw you?
I've got merchandise to sell, you've got buyers.

32:34.680 --> 32:37.706
It's that simple. I just want to know
what I'm getting into.

32:37.783 --> 32:40.547
Okay. Okay. Security is airtight.

32:40.619 --> 32:42.587
The warehouse
is not connected to us.

32:42.655 --> 32:45.146
We keep the, uh,
weapons there till we ship.

32:45.224 --> 32:48.125
- The cops come, they can't arrest anybody.
- A dead drop.

32:48.194 --> 32:51.220
So what if someone tries
to steal your merchandise?

32:51.297 --> 32:54.061
Nobody knows where it is.
Just the family.

32:56.602 --> 32:58.593
Out.

33:11.617 --> 33:14.051
There. Now you see the operation.

33:15.254 --> 33:17.188
Not bad.

33:17.256 --> 33:20.248
On the warehouse front.
What about security?

33:20.326 --> 33:22.260
We have no problems with cops.

33:22.328 --> 33:25.388
We have cops on the payroll.
They let us know ifthere's a problem.

33:25.464 --> 33:27.864
Great. M1 A.308.

33:27.933 --> 33:29.867
Nicely balanced.

33:32.104 --> 33:33.366
Special Forces.

33:33.439 --> 33:35.771
Airport security.

33:35.841 --> 33:37.741
- We have a guy.
- Reliable?

33:37.810 --> 33:39.801
Yeah.

33:39.879 --> 33:43.280
If not, we, uh,
how do they say, uh--

33:43.349 --> 33:44.907
We liquidate him.

33:44.984 --> 33:48.249
F.N.P.-90 with halo sighting.

33:49.155 --> 33:51.623
State ofthe art.
Very nice.

33:51.690 --> 33:56.389
Looks likeyou have things wired here.
So, arewe gonna do some business?

34:02.802 --> 34:06.329
Afterwe send out the shipment...

34:06.405 --> 34:08.600
we make a deal, you and I.

34:08.674 --> 34:11.973
Weput it together,
then I take the deal to myfather.

34:14.880 --> 34:17.178
Trust me.

34:17.248 --> 34:19.342
You're doing him a favor.

34:20.920 --> 34:22.911
Shall we?

34:23.922 --> 34:25.914
You want me to talk to them again?

34:25.991 --> 34:29.051
They'll kill me.
You see what they did.

34:29.128 --> 34:31.755
I thought the plan
was to find the guns and call the cops.

34:31.831 --> 34:35.790
- That plan won't work anymore.
- They've got cops on the payroll,Jake.

34:35.868 --> 34:40.429
Ifyou want to get out ofthis,
it's your best chance, foryour family.

34:40.505 --> 34:42.496
What do I do?

34:42.574 --> 34:46.875
I think it's about time the Zamar family
learned about Ari's new friend.

34:47.279 --> 34:50.339
[Michael Narrating]Anygood operative
is going to be a bit ofa control freak.

34:50.416 --> 34:52.475
Above all, they don't
want to hear...

34:52.551 --> 34:56.817
that the people they think they own really
belong to someone who can destroy them.

34:56.889 --> 35:00.120
Look. I said I would hel p you.

35:00.192 --> 35:02.251
I gotta help your friends now?
I can't do this.

35:02.328 --> 35:05.388
What are you talking about?
What friend?

35:05.464 --> 35:08.456
Steve something.
He said he worked with Ari.

35:08.534 --> 35:12.402
He checked out the logs,
had me show him the airport.

35:12.471 --> 35:16.805
He said I belonged to him now. What the hell
is that supposed to mean? I belong to him?

35:16.876 --> 35:20.368
He had my Social Security number,
my passport information.

35:20.446 --> 35:24.075
- He had all kinds ofstuff
aboutyou guys too. Pictures.
- What areyou talking about?

35:24.150 --> 35:27.347
I don't know what's happening to me.
I want my life back. Give me my life back.

35:27.419 --> 35:29.717
Shut up! Shut up!

35:29.788 --> 35:32.018
Ari. Who is this person?

35:33.893 --> 35:35.952
Who is he?

35:36.028 --> 35:38.826
I don't know. Okay?
That's what I'm saying.

35:38.898 --> 35:40.832
He said he was friends with Ari.

35:40.900 --> 35:43.926
I don't know anything.

35:45.337 --> 35:47.828
Get out. Get out.

35:47.907 --> 35:49.841
Get out!

35:54.914 --> 35:57.178
Ari, what didyou do?

35:59.818 --> 36:03.413
I told you never to talk to anyone.

36:03.489 --> 36:06.947
No, no. This is my deal.
I did this on my own.

36:07.026 --> 36:10.427
A deal? Who asked you
to do this deal?

36:10.496 --> 36:12.930
Who is this friend? Huh?

36:12.998 --> 36:16.525
What? What?
He has documents about us. Pictures!

36:21.006 --> 36:23.566
Met him at a club.
He came to me.

36:23.642 --> 36:26.372
What does he know?
Did you tell him anything?

36:26.445 --> 36:28.379
Did you show him anything?

36:28.447 --> 36:30.472
I showed him the warehouse.

36:30.549 --> 36:33.245
He'd--I showedhim a little.

36:33.319 --> 36:35.913
But-- But it's okay.
He was blindfolded.

36:35.988 --> 36:38.286
He just wanted to see
the operation and--

36:38.357 --> 36:40.291
- Ilan.
- Yeah.

36:40.359 --> 36:42.384
Go to the warehouse. Now!

36:43.462 --> 36:45.430
Come, you fool!

36:45.497 --> 36:47.124
[ Eli Speaking
F.oreign Language ]

36:58.711 --> 37:01.475
- Was that okay?
- [ F.iona ] Perfect. Michael trainedyou well.

37:03.215 --> 37:04.807
They're on their way, Michael.

37:11.156 --> 37:15.092
I am telling you. He was the real deal.
Okay? He had a trunk full of C-4.

37:15.160 --> 37:18.186
[ Foreign Language ]
Someone is there.

37:19.431 --> 37:21.797
It's all gone.

37:21.867 --> 37:23.892
Everything.

37:33.545 --> 37:35.536
[Michael Narrating]
There's nothing worse foranyone...

37:35.614 --> 37:39.175
who's spent time in intelligence work
than being up against a ghost.

37:44.423 --> 37:46.448
You can deal with
an enemyyou know...

37:46.525 --> 37:48.493
but an enemyyou don't know?

37:48.560 --> 37:50.551
[ Car Engine Starts ]

37:56.402 --> 37:59.530
He could be a competitor
who knows all aboutyour operation.

38:10.883 --> 38:14.842
Could be law enforcement
getting ready to bustyou.

38:14.920 --> 38:20.017
Could be a foreign agent settingyou up
in some deep spy game.

38:21.093 --> 38:23.391
Your only option is to disappear.

38:23.462 --> 38:26.863
Steve Rem i ngton.
He said he was Special Forces.

38:26.932 --> 38:29.366
Try again. He could be
using another name.

38:31.637 --> 38:34.003
Enough, Ari!

38:34.073 --> 38:36.337
Let's go!

38:36.408 --> 38:38.273
Get moving!

38:44.316 --> 38:46.307
[ Ringing ]

38:52.725 --> 38:55.387
As long as they think Steve Remington
owns you, you're safe.

38:55.461 --> 38:58.624
As far as they know, there's a mystery man
out there who can destroy them...

38:58.697 --> 39:00.824
and you're his property.

39:00.899 --> 39:02.890
Thankyou.

39:02.968 --> 39:05.402
Yeah. I'm not here
fishing forthanks.

39:05.471 --> 39:07.405
You need to understand
the situation.

39:07.473 --> 39:09.566
Eli will have his ear
to the ground forever.

39:09.641 --> 39:11.802
Ifword gets out he got conned...

39:11.877 --> 39:14.675
you're dead.

39:14.747 --> 39:18.808
You guys look so serious. Come on.
It's not that hard, man.

39:18.884 --> 39:23.344
I mean, secrets are what keep
a family strong, right?

39:24.923 --> 39:26.914
Something like that.

39:28.560 --> 39:30.551
[DoorOpens ]

39:39.738 --> 39:42.730
I mean, look. I'm just glad
thatyou guys are finally happy.

39:42.808 --> 39:45.003
I gotta tell you, though,
when I busted into Mike's place...

39:45.077 --> 39:47.011
I didn't know
ifl was gonna find anything...

39:47.079 --> 39:49.912
and then I find this document here
in a hidey-hole under the sink.

39:49.982 --> 39:52.177
I don't know.
Maybe he's as badasyou guys say.

39:52.251 --> 39:57.621
We sent this up the ladder. This document's
classified. Westen shouldn't have had this.

39:57.689 --> 39:59.623
They're looking for leaks.

39:59.691 --> 40:02.524
Well, that's nice, but the point here, fellas,
is I brought home the bacon.

40:02.594 --> 40:04.763
Okay? You got prime goods
on my buddy Mike right there.

40:04.763 --> 40:05.161
Okay? You got prime goods
on my buddy Mike right there.

40:05.230 --> 40:07.755
We're offthe case, Sam.
This thing's serious enough...

40:07.833 --> 40:10.301
Washington's sending
someone else down.

40:10.369 --> 40:12.098
Westen's someone else's problem now.

40:12.171 --> 40:14.105
Yeah?

40:14.173 --> 40:16.107
New surveillance?
What--What department?

40:16.175 --> 40:18.439
Don't know. Don't care.

40:18.510 --> 40:20.478
Enjoyyour lunch, Sam.

40:20.546 --> 40:22.912
- Seeyou around.
- Yeah.

40:24.016 --> 40:26.382
Huh.

40:26.452 --> 40:28.920
Thanks, fellas.

40:28.987 --> 40:30.978
I'm gonna miss you guys, you know.

40:31.056 --> 40:33.684
[ Beeping ]

40:33.759 --> 40:35.693
- Mike.
- Hey, Sam.

40:35.761 --> 40:40.255
Yeah. Good news and bad news.
Uh, good news is your F.B.I. tail got pulled.

40:40.332 --> 40:42.630
Bad news is they're sending
someone new down.

40:42.701 --> 40:45.499
- Sounds heavy.
- Thanks, Sam. Who's the new surveillance?

40:45.571 --> 40:48.267
Hell ifl know.
Oh, uh, there's more good news.

40:48.340 --> 40:52.242
Theywere so eager to get rid ofyou,
they dropped three 20s on a 1 0-buck tab.

40:52.311 --> 40:54.802
- Luckyyou.
- All right. Checkyou later.

41:00.786 --> 41:02.777
Hi there.

41:02.855 --> 41:04.990
Myfriendsjust abandoned me. Anychance
I couldgetyou to keep me company?

41:04.990 --> 41:06.685
Myfriendsjust abandoned me. Any chance
