41:06.758 --> 41:09.522
Maybe.

41:11.096 --> 41:14.361
- I 'm Sam.
- Hi. I 'm Veronica.

41:14.433 --> 41:16.162
What are we drinkin'?

41:19.371 --> 41:22.397
- I knew it wasn't gonna be in there.
- Well, she said it was in here.

41:22.474 --> 41:24.533
- Of course, she--Well, it's not.
- I--

41:26.745 --> 41:28.736
Soyou stop arguing now?

41:28.814 --> 41:31.942
- Ma, it doesn't mention the car in the will.
- I know.

41:32.017 --> 41:34.042
- You know?
- I wanted Michael to know...

41:34.119 --> 41:36.417
that his father remembered
him in the end...

41:36.488 --> 41:38.456
and, Nate, you spent
more time with him.

41:38.524 --> 41:41.459
- You lied.
- Yeah.

41:41.527 --> 41:43.586
Makes sense.

41:43.662 --> 41:45.755
You know what, Nate?
Fine.

41:47.332 --> 41:49.425
I'll flipyou for it.

41:50.869 --> 41:52.803
All right. Heads.

41:55.941 --> 41:57.966
Yeah. Of course.

41:58.043 --> 41:59.533
You know what?

41:59.611 --> 42:02.671
You won it fair and square, Bro.

42:12.190 --> 42:14.454
Now, you see, Michael?
You're too hard on him.

42:14.526 --> 42:17.086
He can be so sweet.

42:17.162 --> 42:20.290
- I just want us to be family.
- I know, Mom.

42:20.365 --> 42:22.299
I know.

42:22.367 --> 42:24.631
He just stole mywallet. Nate!

